Date: 2014-6-10

Removed specialised reading/writing functions, adds xRead and xWrite.

Date: 2014-6-11

Enhancements:

* Added xRead, which reads a file as a single string.

* Added xWrite, which writes a single string to a file.

Documentation:

* Updated xAddKey examples to exploit partial application.













Kiwi 0.19.0
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Date: 2014-6-10

A minor update. Adds xLastAs, fixes a bug in xFirstAs...xFourthAs.

Date: 2014-6-10

Enhancements:

* Added xLastAs, which sets the last value of a collection.

Bug Fixes:

* xFirstAs ... xFourthAs could not be correctly partially-applied. This is fixed, and
a future version of Kiwi will guard against these errors.

Documentation:

Package Internals:

* Updated the xVal test to work correctly with Rscript testing commands;
tests now run correctly from the command line.

* Added Rscript to run a single unit test.

